---
// FAQ Modal Component
---

<!-- FAQ Modal -->
<div id="faq-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[9999] hidden" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4">
        <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-3xl rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-y-auto max-h-[95vh] sm:max-h-[90vh] relative">
        <div class="modal-content p-4 sm:p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 sticky top-0 bg-white z-10 pb-4 border-b border-secondary/20">
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-playfair font-semibold text-darktext">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
                <button class="modal-close p-2 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 text-darktext" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQ Content -->
            <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
                <!-- Basic Questions -->
                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>What are Eyelash Extensions?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Think of them as magical butterfly wings for your eyes! Our extensions are premium synthetic fibers, individually attached to your natural lashes. They're lightweight, curled to perfection, and designed to enhance your natural beauty while looking completely natural.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12 2C10.34 2 9 3.34 9 5C9 6.66 10.34 8 12 8C13.66 8 15 6.66 15 5C15 3.34 13.66 2 12 2ZM21 9H15V22H13V16H11V22H9V9H3V7H21V9Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Will It Damage My Natural Lashes?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Not at all! Like the gentle spirits of the forest, our extensions are designed to live in harmony with your natural lashes. When applied correctly by our skilled artists and properly cared for, they won't cause any damage. Your natural lashes will continue their normal growth cycle.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M20.71 7.04C21.1 6.65 21.1 6 20.71 5.63L18.37 3.29C18 2.9 17.35 2.9 16.96 3.29L15.12 5.12L18.87 8.87M3 17.25V21H6.75L17.81 9.93L14.06 6.18L3 17.25Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>How Are Eyelash Extensions Applied?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>It's like painting a masterpiece! Our artists carefully attach each extension to a single natural lash using special adhesive. You'll lie comfortably with your eyes closed while we work our magic, typically for about 2 hours for a full set.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,17.5C14.33,17.5 16.3,16.04 17.11,14H6.89C7.69,16.04 9.67,17.5 12,17.5M8.5,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 10,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 8.5,8A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 7,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 8.5,11M15.5,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 17,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 15.5,8A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 14,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 15.5,11M12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20M12,2C6.47,2 2,6.5 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Will the Service Hurt?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Not at all! Like floating on a cloud, the process is completely painless. You'll likely find it so relaxing that many clients drift off to sleep during their appointment. Your eyes stay comfortably closed throughout the entire process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,20A8,8 0 0,0 20,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,4A8,8 0 0,0 4,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,20M12,2A10,10 0 0,1 22,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,22C6.47,22 2,17.5 2,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,2M12.5,7V12.25L17,14.92L16.25,16.15L11,13V7H12.5Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>How Long Will My Eyelash Extensions Last?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like the changing seasons, your lash extensions naturally follow your lash growth cycle. With proper care, they can last 4-6 weeks before needing a fill. Each natural lash has its own growth cycle, so extensions will gradually shed with your natural lashes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,3L2,12H5V20H19V12H22L12,3M11.5,18H10V14H8L11.5,9.5V18M13.5,18V9.5L17,14H15V18H13.5Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>What Can I Do to Make My Lashes Stay Longer?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like tending to a magical garden! Keep them clean and dry for the first 24 hours, avoid oil-based products, brush them gently daily with a clean spoolie, and sleep on your back when possible. Treat them with care, and they'll stay beautiful longer!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,9A3,3 0 0,0 9,12A3,3 0 0,0 12,15A3,3 0 0,0 15,12A3,3 0 0,0 12,9M12,17A5,5 0 0,1 7,12A5,5 0 0,1 12,7A5,5 0 0,1 17,12A5,5 0 0,1 12,17M12,4.5C7,4.5 2.73,7.61 1,12C2.73,16.39 7,19.5 12,19.5C17,19.5 21.27,16.39 23,12C21.27,7.61 17,4.5 12,4.5Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>What Will They Look Like on Me?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like a custom-crafted spell, we'll design your perfect look! We consider your eye shape, natural lash condition, and desired style to create a look that enhances your natural beauty. From subtle enhancement to dramatic glamour, we'll find your perfect match.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M9,10V12H7V10H9M13,10V12H11V10H13M17,10V12H15V10H17M19,3H18V1H16V3H8V1H6V3H5C3.89,3 3,3.9 3,5V19A2,2 0 0,0 5,21H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,19V5A2,2 0 0,0 19,3M19,19H5V8H19V19Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>How Often Do I Need to Get Them Touched-Up?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like the rhythm of nature, most clients come every 2-3 weeks for fills to keep their lashes looking full and beautiful. The timing can vary based on your natural lash cycle and how well you care for them.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M20.71,4.63L19.37,3.29C19,2.9 18.35,2.9 17.96,3.29L9,12.25L11.75,15L20.71,6.04C21.1,5.65 21.1,5 20.71,4.63M7,14A3,3 0 0,0 4,17C4,18.31 2.84,19 2,19C2.92,20.22 4.5,21 6,21A4,4 0 0,0 10,17A3,3 0 0,0 7,14Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Can I Still Wear My Usual Makeup?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, but with a magical twist! Avoid oil-based products and waterproof mascara. Regular mascara isn't needed, but if you want to use eye makeup, gentle, water-based products are fine. Just be extra gentle when removing it!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Advanced Questions -->
                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,3.25C12.41,3.25 12.75,3.59 12.75,4C12.75,4.41 12.41,4.75 12,4.75C7.58,4.75 4,8.33 4,12.75C4,17.17 7.58,20.75 12,20.75C16.42,20.75 20,17.17 20,12.75C20,11.78 19.78,10.85 19.37,10H17.74C18.14,10.64 18.37,11.39 18.37,12.19C18.37,15.23 15.93,17.67 12.89,17.67C9.85,17.67 7.41,15.23 7.41,12.19C7.41,9.15 9.85,6.71 12.89,6.71C14.07,6.71 15.17,7.09 16.09,7.74L17.5,6.34C16.27,5.42 14.74,4.87 13.12,4.87C12.75,4.87 12.37,4.89 12,4.93C12,4.44 12,3.95 12,3.46L12,3.25M21,3V9H15L17.93,6.06C16.73,5.06 15.24,4.43 13.6,4.23C13.21,4.19 12.81,4.17 12.41,4.17V2.17C12.81,2.17 13.21,2.19 13.6,2.23C16.04,2.5 18.22,3.54 19.93,5.15L21,3M12,8C10.22,8 8.78,9.44 8.78,11.22C8.78,13 10.22,14.44 12,14.44C13.78,14.44 15.22,13 15.22,11.22C15.22,9.44 13.78,8 12,8Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Can I Get Them Wet Right Away?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like waiting for a potion to brew, give it 24 hours! After that initial period, you can resume your normal activities. The adhesive needs this time to fully cure and create a strong, lasting bond.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M9,3V4H4V6H5V19A2,2 0 0,0 7,21H17A2,2 0 0,0 19,19V6H20V4H15V3H9M7,6H17V19H7V6M9,8V17H11V8H9M13,8V17H15V8H13Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>How Should I Take Care of My New Eyelash Extensions?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like caring for a magical creature! Keep them clean with gentle, oil-free cleanser, brush them daily with a clean spoolie, avoid rubbing your eyes, and be gentle when washing your face. We'll provide you with detailed care instructions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,1L8,5H11V14H13V5H16M18,23H6C4.89,23 4,22.1 4,21V9A2,2 0 0,1 6,7H9V9H6V21H18V9H15V7H18A2,2 0 0,1 20,9V21A2,2 0 0,1 18,23Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Are the Adhesive Chemicals You Use Safe?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! Like the purest spring water, our adhesives are medical-grade, fume-free, and specifically formulated for use around the eyes. We use only the highest quality products that have been thoroughly tested for safety.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M10,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 11.5,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 10,12.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 8.5,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 10,9.5M14.5,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 16,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 14.5,12.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 13,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,1 14.5,9.5M17,17H7V15.5C7,15.5 10,14 12.5,14C15,14 17.5,15.5 17.5,15.5V17Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>How Long Will the Service Last?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like watching clouds drift by, your first full set appointment may take about 1.5 hours. Fill appointments typically take 1 hour. We take our time to ensure each lash is perfectly placed for the best results.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,20C7.59,20 4,16.41 4,12C4,7.59 7.59,4 12,4C16.41,4 20,7.59 20,12C20,16.41 16.41,20 12,20M16.59,7.58L10,14.17L7.41,11.59L6,13L10,17L18,9L16.59,7.58Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>What Look Is Best for Me?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like choosing your perfect wand, we'll help find your ideal style! During your consultation, we'll consider your eye shape, lifestyle, and preferences to recommend the perfect length, curl, and volume for your unique beauty.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M3,5A2,2 0 0,1 5,3H19A2,2 0 0,1 21,5V19A2,2 0 0,1 19,21H5C3.89,21 3,20.1 3,19V5M7,7V17H9V7H7M11,7V17H13V7H11M15,7V17H17V7H15Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>What Length of Lashes Should I Get?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like finding the perfect balance in nature, we'll help you choose! Most clients look best with lengths between 9-13mm, but we'll consider your eye shape, natural lash strength, and desired look to find your ideal length.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
                    <button class="faq-question w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false">
                        <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M13,9H18.5L13,3.5V9M6,2H14L20,8V20A2,2 0 0,1 18,22H6C4.89,22 4,21.1 4,20V4C4,2.89 4.89,2 6,2M15,18V16H6V18H15M18,14V12H6V14H18Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h4>Why Do My Lashes Lay Sideways After a Few Weeks?</h4>
                        <svg class="faq-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Like leaves in the wind, this can happen when your natural lash starts to grow and rotate. Regular fills and proper care, including gentle daily brushing, help keep them aligned. We can also adjust the curl type to prevent this.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-card">
